		<div class="navigation">
			<div class="alignleft">« <a href="/blog/2008/05/13/breaking-news-from-the-white-house-cook-book/" title="previous post: Breaking news from the White House (Cook Book)…">Breaking news from the White House (Cook Book)...</a></div>	
			
