<p>Happy Baking!</p>
<p>MaryJane @ The Baker’s Hotline</p>
<p><strong>Also could have been your batter was ultra-cold; or you used slightly less sugar (more sugar, more spread); or maybe you didn’t use large eggs? Lots of tiny variables… Sound slike you need to experiment again (YUM)! – PJH</strong></p>
 

